summary: Who doesn\'t love the Dawnbreaker? But it\'s a really shitty weapon. Not anymore!
descriptionHtml:
This mod adjusts the stats of the Dawnbreaker so it\'s finally a useful weapon. You can get it by completing the Quest: The Break of Dawn.

It does greater damage, critical hit, weights less and is (a bit) magic resistant!

installs like any other small mod. Please use Nexus Mod Manager for easier use.

Could conflict with other Dawnbreaker mods (Not Dawnguard mods. The sword Dawnbreaker)
author: AlvinTheBest
